highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 260 weeks straight.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Sacrifice” is the highest at #16.
“Light Switch” by Charlie Puth is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #19.
“Formula” by Labrinth is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 49 spots at #114.
